\par \pard\plain \qj\keep\keepn \f4\fs26\lang2057 By transferring flags, you can add Sneak, Hide, and other flags to a player. For a complete list, see values.h under CHAR_FLAG_XXX.
\par Transferring flags do not have the same impact on the game, as boosting abilities. Count one to two flags as one point of ability in {\field{\*\fldinst  REF _Ref289706901 \\* MERGEFORMAT }{\fldrslt Table }}
 above. Use a price multiplier of 1.5 for each flag transferred.
\par 
\par A macro \ldblquote CHAR_FLAG_TRANSFER(flag)\rdblquote  is available.
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs30\lang2057 7.5.1\tab}\pard\plain \s3\sb240\sl360\slmult0\keep\keepn{\*\pn \pnlvl3\pndec\pnprev1\pnstart1\pnsp144 {\pntxtb .}}\f4\fs30\lang2057 Example
